OL,6,FPanel chair Marc Cavey said: "The
OL,7,Fpanel finds that the conduct of Mr
OL,8,FKhan fell significantly short of the
OL,9,Fstandards expected of the profession.
OL,11,F"The findings of misconduct are
OL,12,Fserious as they include a breach of
OL,13,Fprofessional boundaries with pupils.
OL,15,F"This means that Mr Aqib Khan is
OL,16,Fprohibited from teaching indefinitely
OL,17,Fand cannot teach in any school, sixth
OL,18,Fform college, relevant youth
OL,19,Faccommodation or children's home in
OL,20,FEngland."
